            . On the 24th of February I was against the <placeName id="t18300415-374-crimeloc2026">Rose-inn, Smithfield</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300415-374-crimeloc2026" type="placeName" value="Rose-inn, Smithfield"></interp>
